name: Timetastrophe - Game Version
description:
When the second-ever Kenney Jam (2018) came around, I ended up with little time to actually work on anything. Rainstorms in the desert, power outages and a UPS bursting into flames were just a few of the exciting adventures I had.

In the end, I had about 12 hours out of three days. And I made a UFO you could fly around over a nicely scrolling background and some little wandering aliens you couldn't do anything with. Pretty, but I ran out of time for any "game play".

This is my attempt to come back to it and finish it to a playable state. Here's hoping!
